snippet.title: Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek - Lyrical | The Devil | Darshan | Prakash Veer | B Ajaneesh Loknath
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Kannada

Presenting the Lyrical of ''Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek'' from the much-awaited film ''The Devil'' featuring Challenging Star Darshan. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil. Tune in now and feel the vibe. 

Song Credits:
Song Name : Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek
Music Composed, Arranged & Programmed By : B Ajaneesh Loknath
Singer : Deepak Blue
Lyrics : Aniruddha Sastry
Choreographer : Santhu Master
Additional Vocals : B Ajaneesh Loknath, Aniruddha Sastry & Group
Keyboard : B Ajaneesh Loknath, V Sukumar
Rhythm : Ricky D’Costa, Kalyan Chakravarthy, Sukumar V, B Ajaneesh Loknath
Mixed & Mastered By : Sanjay Kumar M P, Renu Digi Studio, Bangalore
Music Production : C R Bobby, B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios Bangalore

Movie Credits:
Starring : Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai, Mahesh Manjrekar, Achyuth Kumar, Sharmila Mandre.
Produced by: J Jayamma & Saregama
Directed by: Prakash Veer
Executive Producer : Thashwini Veer
Dialogue : Kanth Raj S S
Direction Department : Mohan Malagi, M S Abishaik, B. Thimme Gowdaa, Purnima Deshpande, Mallik R, Bharath, Chandrakumar, Yuvraj Hemanth, Sanjana Sudhakarr
Director Of Photography (DOP) : Sudhakarr S Raj
Music Director : B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios
Editor : Harish Komme
Art Director : Mohan B Kere
Action Director : Ram Lakshman
Colourist : Ashwath
Post Production : Annapurna Studios
Managers : Suresh K Mysore, Jagadish Rao R.
Still Photography : Kadur Raghu & Kadur Yogi
Lyrical Video : Gowtham Raj (Single Frame Studio)
Poster Design : Ashwin Ramesh (Win Designs)
PRO : Sudhindra Venkatesh

Lyrics:
Rap:
Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
He Breaks All Time Records

Pallavi:
Nammovrene Nange Bossu
Nanu Badkod For The Fansu
Khaasa Aadre Daasa Naanu
Dosti Nibhaaisu

First Day First Show Theatre Alli
Damaal Dimeel Soundinalli !!
Celebration Maadovr Nijvaad Celebritiesu

Hasividdare Saadhne Maadona
Kashta Padovrge Keerti Nidhaana
Namma Bhaashene Nange Pradhaana
Nera Nudile Helteen Kelanna

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek

Rap:
Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
Forever Record Breaks

Charanam 1:
Cut-Out Andre Naan Antaare
Daulat Ella… No Chance

Yaariginta Naaven Kammi
Anta Aagu… Advance

Ille Hutti Ille Beledu Niyattaagi Ille Duddu
Oorudhdhaara Maadovr Naavu Pakka Localsu!

Yeshte Saahukaara Idru Oorigoore Kondkondidru
Nanna Preetsovr Maatra Nange Celebritiesu

Yene Aagogli
Cho-Ninna Bidovr Naavalla

Nanna Mansalli
Cho-Hachcheyaagirteev Naavella

Beda Namage Berevr Kathe Puraana
Nera Nudile Matte Helteen Kelanna

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek

|| Rap Repeat ||

Charanam 2:
Oyy
Cho-Yenappa
Actually En Gotta Chinna
Cho-Helappa

Ninna Belavanige Ninna Kaiyyalle
Make Your Future Brightu!
Hit Aagodmele Nam Hudga Annovrge
Don’t Need To Be Sweetu!

Prathibhege Illi Kone Illa..
KaleLyoru Kammi Illa…

Nuggi Neevu Munde Bandu Nintre…
Nimge Yashassu

Akkapakkadavra Maatu Keli..
Addressgildang Aagogbedi…
Nimma Nambirovrigella
Neeve Taane The Bossu!!

Nimma Preetige Chiraruni Naa
Ella Nammovre Anta Baalona

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!

|| Rap Repeat ||

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!


Label: Saregama India Limited, A RPSG Group Company

To buy the original and virus free track, visit www.saregama.com
Follow us on: YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/user/Saregamakannada
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Saregamakannada
X: https://twitter.com/saregamasouth

#ChallengingStarDarshan #IdreNemdiyaagIrbek #TheDevil #BAjaneeshLoknath #SaregamaKannada

Turn up the volume because it’s time to groove on the beats of #BadliSiHawaHai! 

Straight from the crazy world of The Ba***ds of Bollywood , the series features Bobby Deol, Lakshya, Sahher Bambba, Manoj Pahwa, Mona Singh, Manish Chaudhari, Raghav Juyal, Anya Singh, Vijayant Kohli, Gautami Kapoor and Rajat Bedi. Written and directed by Aryan Khan and produced by Gauri Khan, this Netflix series is presented by Red Chillies Entertainment.

snippet.title: CLASSIC HACKER IS LIVE | The ultimate Xtreme Challenge with crow
snippet.description:
Gear up for the Hero Xtreme Challenge Month with Day 1 featuring the Hero Xtreme 250R! Powered by a 250cc engine  this bike accelerates from 0 to 60 in just 3.2 seconds, giving you the thrill of speed and control. 

With Dual Channel ABS for safety, a race-ready drag timer, and a smooth suspension system, the Xtreme 250R is built to perform, both on the road and in the game. 

Join us as we push the limits of power and precision with every ride and every shot. Don’t miss out on this epic challenge! #HeroXtreme250R #ChallengeTheExtreme #Hero

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema’s first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema’s first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

सुन्दरकांड” – श्री राम चरित मानस का 5 वा अध्याय/कांड है। सुन्दर कांड (Sundar Kand) को सबसे पहले रामायण में श्री वाल्मीकि जी ने संस्कृत में लिखा था। बाद में तुलसी दस जी ने जब श्री राम चरित मानस लिखी, तो सुन्दर कांड का अवधी भाषा वाला रूप हम सब के सामने आया 
सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।
सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।

सुन्दरकांड” – श्री राम चरित मानस का 5 वा अध्याय/कांड है। सुन्दर कांड (Sundar Kand) को सबसे पहले रामायण में श्री वाल्मीकि जी ने संस्कृत में लिखा था। बाद में तुलसी दस जी ने जब श्री राम चरित मानस लिखी, तो सुन्दर कांड का अवधी भाषा वाला रूप हम सब के सामने आया 
सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।
सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।

Background dancers from @ramzat khelaiya reloaded 
add the perfect spark to every frame.

Cinematically captured by our talented videography crew, including 
-Vansh and Prit

Lyrics Of This Song:

ઓ મારી વાલી રે


લે ફરરર ફૂદડી.. ફરી લે ને ફૂદડી..
લે ફરરર ફૂદડી.. ફરી લે ને ફૂદડી..


ઓ મારી વાલી રે.. 
ભઈબંધો મારા તારી કસમ ખવડાવે..(2)
કસમ કેમ તોડું ઓ કોયલ રાણી 
ગર્લફ્રેન્ડ નઇ બનાવુ ઘરવાળી..

લે ફરરર ફૂદડી.. ફરી લે ને ફૂદડી..
લે ફરરર ફૂદડી.. ફરી લે ને ફૂદડી.....(2)..

હે..તને રમતા જોઈ ગરબાને રાસે
મારુ મન મોહી ગયું..
હે તેતો રમતા જુમતા ગરબા ના તાલે
મારુ મન મોહી લીધુ...

હો નજીક આવ તું દૂર સુ ભાગે
તારી મારી જોડી એક નંબર લાગે..
ઓય સાંભળ ને..

ઓ મારી વાલી રે..
મારા ભઈબંધ તને ભાભી કેવા માંગે..(2)
દિલ એનું કેમ તોડુ.. ઓ દિલની રાણી 
ગર્લફ્રેન્ડ નઇ તું છે મારી ઘરવાળી..

ઓ મારી વાલી રે..
ગરબે રમીશું ને આખી રાત ઝુમશુ..(2)
સાથ તારો નઇછોડુ ઓ મેનારાની
ગરબાની નઇ લાઈફ પાર્ટનર તું મારી..

લે ફરરર ફૂદડી.. ફરી લે ને ફૂદડી..
લે ફરરર ફૂદડી.. ફરી લે ને ફૂદડી.....(2)..

માયા તારી લાગી રે..
સુતેલા અરમાનો મારા રે જાગે..(2)
તારા નામ પાછળ જો મારું નામ લાગે..
તારા સિવાય મન બીજું શું માંગે..

લે ફરરર ફૂદડી.. ફરી લે ને ફૂદડી..
લે ફરરર ફૂદડી.. ફરી લે ને ફૂદડી.....(2)..

snippet.title: #Mani Meraj | Marne Ke Baad Pyar Hua | Vannu D Great | Shahbaz Khan | Chand Jee | New Sad Song
snippet.description:
❗कृपया ध्यान दें:❗
इस गाने के सभी कॉपीराइट Trimurti Music World के पास सुरक्षित हैं। कोई भी व्यक्ति या चैनल इस गाने को बिना अनुमति के अपने प्लेटफॉर्म पर री-अपलोड न करे।
🚫 ऐसा करने पर आपके चैनल पर Copyright Strike की कार्रवाई की जाएगी।
🙏 कृपया हमारी मेहनत का सम्मान करें।

"Marne Ke Baad Pyar Hua" एक दिल को छू जाने वाला Bhojpuri Sad Song है, जिसे अपनी soulful आवाज़ में गाया है Chand Jee ने। इस इमोशनल लव स्टोरी में Mani Meraj और Vannu D Great ने फीचरिंग में शानदार अभिनय किया है, वहीं Shahbaz Khan ने विलेन का दमदार किरदार निभाया है।

 Mani Meraj | Marne Ke Baad Pyar Hua | Vannu D Great | Shahbaz Khan | Chand Jee | Sad Song
Reel Link https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1483808312972134/
► Feat :- Mani Meraj, Vannu D Great & Shahbaz Khan
► Album :- Marne Ke Bad Pyar Hua

snippet.description:

सीता राम सीता राम कहिए 
राम नाम के हीरे मोती मैं बिखराऊँ
नगरी हो अयोध्या सी रघुकुल 
राम को मांग ले मेरे प्यारे
कण कण में श्री राम हर मन में
श्री राम अमृतवाणी
जितना दिया सरकार ने मुझको 
श्री राम जय राम जय जय राम 
आरती कीजे श्री राम लला की

snippet.description:
Mere Papa Ne Ganpati Laya (Official MV) Krish Mondal | Rupa Pin2 | Ganesh Chaturthi Special 2025

🌺🙏 Mere Papa Ne Ganpati Laya | Ganesh Chaturthi Special Song 2025 🙏🌺

Celebrate the divine arrival of Ganpati Bappa with this heartwarming and festive song! Mere Papa Ne Ganpati Laya beautifully captures the joy, devotion, and excitement of welcoming Lord Ganesha home during the sacred festival of Ganesh Chaturthi. ✨🎶

From the beats of dhol and the chants of “Ganpati Bappa Morya” to the deep emotions of faith and family togetherness, this special track brings alive the spiritual and cultural essence of Ganesh Utsav 2025. 🌸🕉️

🎵 Let this devotional song fill your home with positivity, happiness, and blessings of prosperity, peace, and success as you celebrate the most awaited festival of the year.

✨ Ganpati Bappa Morya! ✨

🎶 SONG CREDITS 
🎤 Singer : Krish Mondal
🎼 Music : Janny Dholi 
🎹 Keys & Banjo: Kamlesh Jadhav
🥁 Rhythm & Percussions: Janny Dholi

snippet.title: हनुमान चालीसा | Hanuman Chalisa | जय हनुमान ज्ञान गुन सागर | Powerful Devotional  | #hanumanchalisa
snippet.description:
🙏 Jai Shree Ram! Jai Hanuman! 🙏

Experience the divine power of Hanuman Chalisa, one of the most sacred and powerful hymns dedicated to Lord Hanuman. Chanting this devotional song daily brings strength, courage, positivity, and protection from all difficulties in life.

🎧 Owner: Er Mk Singh 
🎙️ Singer: Amit Singh Ammy
🎼 Music Director: Ramnyar Tarjan (Dhun Music)
📝 Lyrics: Traditional
📽️ Produced & Distributed By: Spriteck Media ( Sangeet Sanskar)

🌟 Benefits of Listening to Hanuman Chalisa:
✔ Removes negative energy and fears
✔ Grants strength, wisdom, and confidence
✔ Protects from evil forces and obstacles
✔ Brings peace, prosperity, and success
Here are the full lyrics of Hanuman Chalisa in Hindi and English transliteration:

हनुमान चालीसा (Hanuman Chalisa) Lyrics

॥ दोहा ॥
श्रीगुरु चरण सरोज रज, निज मन मुकुर सुधार।
बरनऊं रघुबर बिमल जसु, जो दायकु फल चार॥

बुद्धिहीन तनु जानिके, सुमिरौं पवन-कुमार।
बल बुधि विद्या देहु मोहिं, हरहु कलेश विकार॥

॥ चौपाई ॥

जय हनुमान ज्ञान गुन सागर।
जय कपीस तिहुं लोक उजागर॥

रामदूत अतुलित बल धामा।
अंजनि-पुत्र पवनसुत नामा॥

महावीर विक्रम बजरंगी।
कुमति निवार सुमति के संगी॥

कंचन बरन विराज सुबेसा।
कानन कुंडल कुंचित केसा॥

हाथ वज्र औ ध्वजा विराजे।
कांधे मूंज जनेऊ साजे॥

शंकर सुवन केसरी नंदन।
तेज प्रताप महा जग वंदन॥

विद्यावान गुणी अति चातुर।
राम काज करिबे को आतुर॥

प्रभु चरित्र सुनिबे को रसिया।
राम लखन सीता मन बसिया॥

सूक्ष्म रूप धरि सियहि दिखावा।
विकट रूप धरि लंक जरावा॥

भीम रूप धरि असुर संहारे।
रामचंद्र के काज संवारे॥

लाय सजीवन लखन जियाए।
श्रीरघुबीर हरषि उर लाए॥

रघुपति कीन्ही बहुत बड़ाई।
तुम मम प्रिय भरतहि सम भाई॥

सहस बदन तुम्हरो जस गावैं।
अस कहि श्रीपति कंठ लगावैं॥

सनकादिक ब्रह्मादि मुनीसा।
नारद सारद सहित अहीसा॥

जम कुबेर दिगपाल जहां ते।
कवि कोविद कहि सके कहां ते॥

तुम उपकार सुग्रीवहिं कीन्हा।
राम मिलाय राज पद दीन्हा॥

तुम
📿 Lyrics & Meaning:
This rendition of Hanuman Chalisa is perfect for daily listening, meditation, and prayer to seek the blessings of Bajrang Bali.

F -  सिर में ठोकलका, घर में रोकलका ऊ हे नू याद बड़ी आवे
      हॅस के बोललका, संगवा रहलका ऊ हे नू याद बड़ी आवे

Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, the song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Najariya Najar Se" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

snippet.title: Franklin & Shinchan’s Funny Munnar KSRTC Trip 😂 | GTA 5 Malayalam Part 2
snippet.description:
Franklin & Shinchan continue their Munnar adventure in this GTA 5 Malayalam story! 🚌⛰️  
Trevor’s family is stuck on the roadside, and Franklin helps them using his KSRTC bus. 🚍  
Meanwhile, Shinchan creates chaos while trying to get milk from a cow 🐄🤣 with lots of funny fail moments.  

Later, Franklin and family stop near a river with elephants 🐘🌿 before facing goons demanding money.  
Franklin shows his power in an epic fight 🔥💥 and saves the day!  

Finally, Franklin, Shinchan, and Trevor enjoy the breathtaking hilltop view of Munnar together ❤️.

snippet.title: JALSA | Teaser | Mantra Muugdha | Suryamayee | Sanoj | Manmay Dey | Sarthak | Anupam Patnaik | TM
snippet.description:
Here’s the promo for the most awaited chartbuster of the year! 

Step into the ultimate dance revolution with “Jalsa” – a track built to ignite every floor, fuel every workout, and turn every moment into a celebration! With thunderous beats, electrifying grooves, and melodies that refuse to leave your head, this anthem is more than music – it’s pure energy.


Feel the rush. Own the night. Keep the vibe alive.

Share the groove. Spread the love. This is Jalsa Night! 

Tarang Music is the official music label of Mantra Muugdha.

Song Credits - 

Music Composed & Produced by Ashish Pradhan
Singers : Humane Sagar, Antara Chakraborty 
Lyrics : Manoj Kumar Panda 
Music Arranged & Co - Produced by : Roumyaj Pradhan
Lyrical Video - Roky 
Live Rhythm - Tiny Bhai, Tula Bhai, Manish Da
Guitars & Mandolin - Rupesh Jeevan
Male Chorus : Ashish Pradhan, Roumyaj Pradhan, Abhishek Purohit, Rupesh Jeevan
Female Chorus :  Smrutika Padhy, Shilpi Pati, Sanskruti Sharma, Sai Pragyan Rout
Vocals Recorded by : Sambit Kumar Mohanty at Somesh Studio, Bhubaneswar
Live Rhythm Recorded by Somesh Satpathy at Somesh Studio, Bhubaneswar
Assistant to Somesh Satpathy : Sambit Mohanty, Sambhab Pani

Shoot Mix : Roumyaj Pradhan

Special Thanks : Shruti Prakash Dash

Beautiful Lord Krishna song. Achutam Keshavam - Krishna Darshan To Denge Kabhi Na Kabhi | Krishna Bhajan | कृष्ण भजन #Krishnasong Achyutam Keshavam
भजन : अच्चुतम केशवं कृष्ण दामोदरं, राम नारायणं जानकी वल्लभम।
अच्चुतम केशवं कृष्ण दामोदरं, राम नारायणं जानकी वल्लभम। कौन कहता हे भगवान आते नहीं तुम मीरा के जैसे बुलाते नहीं। कौन कहता है भगवान खाते नहीं, बेर शबरी के जैसे खिलाते नहीं। कौन कहता है भगवान सोते नहीं, माँ यशोदा के जैसे सुलाते नहीं। कौन कहता है भगवान नाचते नहीं, गोपियों की तरह तुम नचाते नहीं। नाम जपते चलो काम करते चलो, हर समय कृष्ण का ध्यान करते चलो। याद आएगी उनको कभी ना कभी, कृष्ण दर्शन तो देंगे कभी ना कभी। अच्चुतम केशवं कृष्ण दामोदरं, राम नारायणं जानकी बल्लभम। राम नारायणं जानकी बल्लभम। 


Bhajan: Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram: 
English Lyrics 
Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram, Ram Narayanam Janki Vallabham। Kaun Kehte Hai Bhagwan Aate Nahi, Tum Meera Ke Jaise Bulate Nahi। Kaun Kehte Hai Bhawan Khate Nahi, Ber Shabri Ke Jaise Khilate Nahi। Kaun Kehte Hai Bhagwan Sote Nahi, Maa Yashoda Ke Jaise Sulate Nahi। Kaun Kehte Hai Bhagwan Nachte Nahi, Gopiyo Ke Jaise Tum Nachate Nahi। Naam Japte Chalo Kaam Karte Chalo, Har Samay Krishna Ka Naam Dharte Chalo। Yaad Aayegi Unko Kabhi Na Kabhi, Krishna Darshan to Denge Kabhi Na Kabhi। Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram, Ram Narayanam Janki Vallabham।
